# Synapse performance

When working on migration/routing throughput, observability, or the user shares `/metrics` or `/api/v1/performance/baseline` output:

Read `.cursor/skills/synapse-performance/SKILL.md` for phase roadmap, bottleneck decision tree, and reference baselines.

**Execution rule:** Finish gaps in phase **N** (ascending order) before starting **N+1**. Skip items only when harmful or explicitly out of scope — document the skip. Do not jump ahead (e.g. Phase 4.5 before Phase 2/3 complete).
